WEBVTT

00:04.992 --> 00:09.338
On this place I own a lease, sir, I am justice of the peace, sir.

00:09.358 --> 00:12.462
The law west of the Pecosall is here.

00:14.145 --> 00:17.870
And you've acted very badly, so the duty went off sadly.

00:18.410 --> 00:21.975
While adown his lily cheeks there rolled a tear.

00:24.819 --> 00:28.684
Now you boys have heard the story of Roy Bean in all his glory.

00:29.506 --> 00:33.531
He was the man who was the justice of the law.

00:34.658 --> 00:36.626
He was handy with his hook, sir.

00:36.646 --> 00:38.815
He was ornery in his look, sir.

00:38.835 --> 00:42.711
And just now I ain't a-tellin' anymore.

